data.description: Welcome to Promontory Pointe Community featuring this Cozy Two-Story end unit 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom condo boasting over 1,700 square feet of living space, with a 2-car attached garage.  This town-house style condo is located in desirable Rancho Belago area of Moreno Valley. Upon entering the condo there’s an open concept with an abundance of natural lighting.  The living room offers a formal dining area, and the family room has built-in surround sound and a cozy fireplace. The spacious kitchen is perfect for cooking and entertaining. The first floor also features a half bath perfect for guest use! Upstairs The master bedroom has a large walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom with double sinks! This condo also features its own private patio area, association pool/spa and is close to freeways, schools and shopping.
